There are plenty of lazy people like me that wake up everyday and go all most of their day without eating. Eating is a very important and essential part of every day life. I believe that you should eat breakfast everyday and I am going to tell you why. 

Everyone always says that breakfast is the most important meal of the day. I believe that is true. You need energy to do everyday tasks. You get this energy from the food you eat. It is important to consume carbs and nutritious foods to begin you day. One good example of this is eggs and bacon. Eggs are considered a super food and also have good protien.

Eating well everyday is essential to your health. If you want to go about your days feeling good you should eat a well balanced meal to start your day. It is important to do this everyday and make it routine. 

If you try to make your body do things when it does not have enough energy, it will begin to search for ways to do these tasks. This takes brain power for you body to talk to all the parts it needs to. When your body does not have this energy it makes things very hard and your body will begin to shut down because it can not keep up. These are things like headaches, body aches, tiredness, and lack of attention. 

If you do not want to have your day and routine to be messed up and have better peace of mind throughout your day. It is essential that you eat a big breakfast. You will feel full longer during the most important parts of your day while being productive. Your body will have all it needs and will have to work less, therefore making life simple and easy.  => I
